description:
𝙒𝙚𝙚𝙠 𝟴- 𝙎𝙤 𝙢𝙖𝙣𝙮 𝙙𝙞𝙛𝙛𝙚𝙧𝙚𝙣𝙩 𝙛𝙚𝙚𝙡𝙞𝙣𝙜𝙨.. 🙃⁣
⁣
I never really want to leave my house anymore wanting to stay healthy & safe but then again I’m always happy & grateful when I’m finally out running some errands because I get to recreate what we considered ‘normal’ not too long ago..⁣
⁣
But then while being out, I see how we are becoming robots..being interrogated, having to stand in specific spots, avoiding close contact, even avoid eye contact 🤐 and then I’m sad.⁣
⁣
On a day to day basis I AM OK 😇 but a lifetime of this? 😳 Bruh (in Starboi’s voice). I dunno man, thinking about our future is scary.. how do you feel about our ‘new normal’ looking like our future normal? 🌈⁣
⁣
